=\"0 0 512 512\"\u003e\u003c!-- Font Awesome Free 5.15.4 by @fontawesome - https://fontawesome.com License - https://fontawesome.com/license/free (Icons: CC BY 4.0, Fonts: SIL OFL 1.1, Code: MIT License) --\u003e\u003cpath d=\"M328 256c0 39.8-32.2 72-72 72s-72-32.2-72-72 32.2-72 72-72 72 32.2 72 72zm104-72c-39.8 0-72 32.2-72 72s32.2 72 72 72 72-32.2 72-72-32.2-72-72-72zm-352 0c-39.8 0-72 32.2-72 72s32.2 72 72 72 72-32.2 72-72-32.2-72-72-72z\"/\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\u003c/button\u003e\r\n    \u003c/div\u003e\r\n  \u003c/div\u003e\r\n  \u003cpre style=\"counter-reset: codeblock;\" class=\"tw-block tw-m-0 tw-p-0\"\u003e\u003ccode \r\n    id=\"codeblock-id-15\" \r\n    class=\"\r\n      chroma \r\n      !tw-block \r\n      tw-p-0\r\n      tw-m-0\r\n      tw-transition-[max-height] \r\n      tw-duration-500 \r\n      tw-ease-in-out \r\n      group-[.is-closed]:!tw-max-h-0 \r\n      group-[.is-wrap]:tw-text-wrap\r\n      tw-overflow-y-hidden\r\n      tw-overflow-x-auto\r\n      tw-scrollbar-thin\r\n      \"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"line\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"cl\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"kr\"\u003eexport\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\"kr\"\u003econst\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\"nx\"\u003eauthInterceptor\u003c/span\u003e: \u003cspan class=\"kt\"\u003eHttpInterceptorFn\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\"o\"\u003e=\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\"p\"\u003e(\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"nx\"\u003ereq\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"p\"\u003e,\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\"nx\"\u003enext\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"p\"\u003e)\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\"o\"\u003e=\u0026gt;\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\"p\"\u003e{\u003c/span\u003e\n\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"line\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"cl\"\u003e  \u003cspan class=\"kr\"\u003econst\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\"nx\"\u003econfig\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\"o\"\u003e=\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\"nx\"\u003einject\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"p\"\u003e(\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"nx\"\u003eAPP_CONFIG\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"p\"\u003e);\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\"c1\"\u003e// We can STILL use DI here!\n\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"line\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"cl\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"c1\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e  \u003cspan class=\"c1\"\u003e// ... wrap request\n\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"line\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"cl\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"c1\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e  \u003cspan class=\"k\"\u003ereturn\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\"nx\"\u003enext\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"p\"\u003e(\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"nx\"\u003ereq\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"p\"\u003e);\u003c/span\u003e\n\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"line\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"cl\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"p\"\u003e};\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/code\u003e\u003c/pre\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003ch2 id=\"wrapping-up-phase-1\" class=\"headerLink\"\u003e\r\n    \u003ca href=\"#wrapping-up-phase-1\" class=\"header-mark\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e5 Wrapping Up Phase 1\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cp\u003eBy the end of Phase 1, we have a \u0026ldquo;shell\u0026rdquo; that is optimized for performance (Zoneless), highly configurable through \u003ccode\u003eInjectionTokens\u003c/code\u003e, and resilient thanks to a global error handling strategy.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eNext up:\u003c/strong\u003e Phase 2, where we tackle Security, functional guards, and our first premium UI components with glassmorphism.\u003c/p\u003e",
        "language": "en"
    },
    {
        "title" : "Angular Enterprise Dashboard - Introduction: A Journey into Modern Web Engineering",
        "date_published" : "2026-02-14T14:40:18+02:00",
        "date_modified" : "2026-02-16T15:01:32+02:00",
        "id" : "https://buffos.github.io/2026-03-14-angular-enterprise-board-part-01/",
        "url" : "https://buffos.github.io/2026-03-14-angular-enterprise-board-part-01/",
        "summary": "In the ever-evolving landscape of web development, staying ahead means embracing the cutting edge. This project, the Angular Enterprise Dashboard, is born from a desire to showcase what is possible with the latest advancements in the Angular ecosystem.\nMore than just a portfolio piece, this dashboard is an exploration of high-performance architecture, reactive state management, and enterprise-grade design patterns.\n",
        "content_html" : "\u003cp\u003eIn the ever-evolving landscape of web development, staying ahead means embracing the cutting edge. This project, the \u003cstrong\u003eAngular Enterprise Dashboard\u003c/strong\u003e, is born from a desire to showcase what is possible with the latest advancements in the Angular ecosystem.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eMore than just a portfolio piece, this dashboard is an exploration of high-performance architecture, reactive state management, and enterprise-grade design patterns.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch2 id=\"the-vision-modern-fast-and-robust\" class=\"headerLink\"\u003e\r\n    \u003ca href=\"#the-vision-modern-fast-and-robust\" class=\"header-mark\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e1 The Vision: Modern, Fast, and Robust\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe core intention of this project is to build a professional-grade dashboard that leverages \u003cstrong\u003eAngular v21+\u003c/strong\u003e to its fullest potential. We are moving away from traditional patterns and embracing the future of the framework:\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch3 id=\"-zoneless-performance\" class=\"headerLink\"\u003e\r\n    \u003ca href=\"#-zoneless-performance\" class=\"header-mark\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e1.1 🚀 Zoneless Performance\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cp\u003eBy utilizing \u003ccode\u003eprovideExperimentalZonelessChangeDetection\u003c/code\u003e, we are stripping away the overhead of Zone.js. This results in faster change detection cycles and a leaner application footprint—essential for the snappiness expected in modern enterprise interfaces.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch3 id=\"-masterful-state-with-signals\" class=\"headerLink\"\u003e\r\n    \u003ca href=\"#-masterful-state-with-signals\" class=\"header-mark\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e1.2 🚥 Masterful State with Signals\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cp\u003eSignals are the heartbeat of this application. From simple component state to complex authentication flows, we use \u003ccode\u003esignal()\u003c/code\u003e, \u003ccode\u003ecomputed()\u003c/code\u003e, and the new \u003ccode\u003eResource\u003c/code\u003e APIs to create a truly reactive and predictable data flow.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch3 id=\"-enterprise-infrastructure\" class=\"headerLink\"\u003e\r\n    \u003ca href=\"#-enterprise-infrastructure\" class=\"header-mark\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e1.3 🏗️ Enterprise Infrastructure\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cp\u003eA project is only as good as its foundation. We\u0026rsquo;ve already implemented:\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eStateless Prerendering (SSG)\u003c/strong\u003e for lighting-fast initial loads and SEO.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eDependency Injection Mastery\u003c/strong\u003e using \u003ccode\u003eInjectionToken\u003c/code\u003e for clean, testable configurations.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eGlobal Resilience\u003c/strong\u003e with a custom global error handling and toast notification system.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eMultilingual Support (i18n)\u003c/strong\u003e with Greek and English integration from day one.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003ch2 id=\"the-roadmap-ahead\" class=\"headerLink\"\u003e\r\n    \u003ca href=\"#the-roadmap-ahead\" class=\"header-mark\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e2 The Roadmap Ahead\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cp\u003eWe are currently in the early phases of development, but the roadmap is ambitious:\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003col\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003ePhase 1: Foundation (Complete)\u003c/strong\u003e - The core infrastructure and zoneless setup.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003ePhase 2: Security \u0026amp; Shell (In Progress)\u003c/strong\u003e - Building a reactive application shell with glassmorphism design and signal-based authentication.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003ePhase 3: Intelligence \u0026amp; Visualization\u003c/strong\u003e - Integrating real-time data fetching with the Resource API and high-performance charts.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003ePhase 4: Dynamic Forms \u0026amp; OCP\u003c/strong\u003e - Implementing flexible, configuration-driven forms following the Open-Closed Principle.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ol\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eStay tuned as we continue to push the boundaries of what Angular can do. This project is not just about building a dashboard; it\u0026rsquo;s about defining a blueprint for the next generation of enterprise web applications.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003chr\u003e",
        "language": "en"
    },
    {
        "title" : "LaTeX: Creating placeholder boxes for mathematical operations",
        "date_published" : "2025-08-27T22:30:43+03:00",
        "date_modified" : "2026-02-16T15:01:32+02:00",
        "id" : "https://buffos.github.io/2025-08-31-latexboxes/",
        "url" : "https://buffos.github.io/2025-08-31-latexboxes/",
        "summary": "Did you ever need empty placeholder boxes in your LaTeX document. I did, and here is a nice way to solve the problem\n",
        "content_html" : "\u003cp\u003eDid you ever need empty placeholder boxes in your LaTeX document. I did, and here is a nice way to solve the problem\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch2 id=\"first-attempt\" class=\"headerLink\"\u003e\r\n    \u003ca href=\"#first-attempt\" class=\"header-mark\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e13 First Attempt\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cp\u003eLet\u0026rsquo;s first start with some basic definitions\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"code-block highlight is-closed show-line-numbers  tw-group tw-my-2\"\u003e\r\n  \u003cdiv class=\"\r\n    \r\n    tw-flex \r\n    tw-flex-row\r\n    tw-flex-1 \r\n    tw-justify-between \r\n    tw-w-full tw-bg-bgColor-secondary\r\n    \"\u003e      \r\n    \u003cbutton \r\n      class=\"\r\n        code-block-button\r\n        tw-mx-2 \r\n        tw-flex\r\n        tw-flex-row\r\n        tw-flex-1\"\r\n      aria-hidden=\"true\"\u003e\r\n          \u003cdiv class=\"group-[.is-open]:tw-rotate-90 tw-transition-[transform] tw-duration-500 tw-ease-in-out print:!tw-hidden tw-w-min tw-h-min tw-my-1 tw-mx-1\"\u003e\u003csvg class=\"icon\"\n    xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 320 512\"\u003e\u003c!-- Font Awesome Free 5.15.4 by @fontawesome - https://fontawesome.com License - https://fontawesome.com/license/free (Icons: CC BY 4.0, Fonts: SIL OFL 1.1, Code: MIT License) --\u003e\u003cpath d=\"M285.476 272.971L91.132 467.314c-9.373 9.373-24.569 9.373-33.941 0l-22.667-22.667c-9.357-9.357-9.375-24.522-.04-33.901L188.505 256 34.484 101.255c-9.335-9.379-9.317-24.544.04-33.901l22.667-22.667c9.373-9.373 24.569-9.373 33.941 0L285.475 239.03c9.373 9.372 9.373 24.568.001 33.941z\"/\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\r\n          \u003cp class=\"tw-select-none !tw-my-1\"\u003eLaTeX\u003c/p\u003e\r\n      \u003c/button\u003e\r\n\r\n   \u003cdiv class=\"tw-flex\"\u003e\r\n      \u003cbutton \r\n        class=\"\r\n          line-number-button\r\n          tw-mx-2 \r\n          tw-hidden \r\n          group-[.is-open]:tw-block \r\n          group-[.show-line-numbers]:tw-text-fgColor-link \r\n          print:!tw-hidden\" \r\n        title=\"Toggle line numbers\"\u003e\u003csvg class=\"icon\"\n    xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 512 512\"\u003e\u003c!-- Font Awesome Free 5.15.4 by @fontawesome - https://fontawesome.com License - https://fontawesome.com/license/free (Icons: CC BY 4.0, Fonts: SIL OFL 1.1, Code: MIT License) --\u003e\u003cpath d=\"M61.77 401l17.5-20.15a19.92 19.92 0 0 0 5.07-14.19v-3.31C84.34 356 80.5 352 73 352H16a8 8 0 0 0-8 8v16a8 8 0 0 0 8 8h22.83a157.41 157.41 0 0 0-11 12.31l-5.61 7c-4 5.07-5.25 10.13-2.8 14.88l1.05 1.93c3 5.76 6.29 7.88 12.25 7.88h4.73c10.33 0 15.94 2.44 15.94 9.09 0 4.72-4.2 8.22-14.36 8.22a41.54 41.54 0 0 1-15.47-3.12c-6.49-3.88-11.74-3.5-15.6 3.12l-5.59 9.31c-3.72 6.13-3.19 11.72 2.63 15.94 7.71 4.69 20.38 9.44 37 9.44 34.16 0 48.5-22.75 48.5-44.12-.03-14.38-9.12-29.76-28.73-34.88zM496 224H176a16 16 0 0 0-16 16v32a16 16 0 0 0 16 16h320a16 16 0 0 0 16-16v-32a16 16 0 0 0-16-16zm0-160H176a16 16 0 0 0-16 16v32a16 16 0 0 0 16 16h320a16 16 0 0 0 16-16V80a16 16 0 0 0-16-16zm0 320H176a16 16 0 0 0-16 16v32a16 16 0 0 0 16 16h320a16 16 0 0 0 16-16v-32a16 16 0 0 0-16-16zM16 160h64a8 8 0 0 0 8-8v-16a8 8 0 0 0-8-8H64V40a8 8 0 0 0-8-8H32a8 8 0 0 0-7.14 4.42l-8 16A8 8 0 0 0 24 64h8v64H16a8 8 0 0 0-8 8v16a8 8 0 0 0 8 8zm-3.91 160H80a8 8 0 0 0 8-8v-16a8 8 0 0 0-8-8H41.32c3.29-10.29 48.34-18.68 48.34-56.44 0-29.06-25-39.56-44.47-39.56-21.36 0-33.8 10-40.46 18.75-4.37 5.59-3 10.84 2.8 15.37l8.58 6.88c5.61 4.56 11 2.47 16.12-2.44a13.44 13.44 0 0 1 9.46-3.84c3.33 0 9.28 1.56 9.28 8.75C51 248.19 0 257.31 0 304.59v4C0 316 5.08 320 12.09 320z\"/\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\u003c/button\u003e\r\n\r\n      \u003cbutton \r\n        class=\"\r\n          wrap-code-button\r\n          tw-select-none \r\n          tw-mx-2 \r\n          tw-hidden \r\n          group-[.is-open]:tw-block \r\n          group-[.is-wrap]:tw-text-fgColor-link \r\n          print:!tw-hidden\" \r\n        title=\"Toggle code wrap\"\u003e\u003csvg class=\"icon\"\n    xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 448 512\"\u003e\u003c!-- Font Awesome Free 5.15.4 by @fontawesome - https://fontawesome.com License - https://fontawesome.com/license/free (Icons: CC BY 4.0, Fonts: SIL OFL 1.1, Code: MIT License) --\u003e\u003cpath d=\"M16 132h416c8.837 0 16-7.163 16-16V76c0-8.837-7.163-16-16-16H16C7.163 60 0 67.163 0 76v40c0 8.837 7.163 16 16 16zm0 160h416c8.837 0 16-7.163 16-16v-40c0-8.837-7.163-16-16-16H16c-8.837 0-16 7.163-16 16v40c0 8.837 7.163 16 16 16zm0 160h416c8.837 0 16-7.163 16-16v-40c0-8.837-7.163-16-16-16H16c-8.837 0-16 7.163-16 16v40c0 8.837 7.163 16 16 16z\"/\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\u003c/button\u003e\r\n      \r\n      \u003cbutton \r\n        class=\"\r\n          copy-code-button\r\n          tw-select-none\r\n          tw-mx-2 \r\n          tw-hidden\r\n          group-[.is-open]:tw-block\r\n          hover:tw-text-fgColor-link \r\n          print:!tw-hidden\"\r\n        title=\"Copy code\"\u003e\r\n          \u003cspan class=\"copy-icon tw-block\"\u003e\u003csvg class=\"icon\"\n    xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 448 512\"\u003e\u003c!-- Font Awesome Free 5.15.4 by @fontawesome - https://fontawesome.com License - https://fontawesome.com/license/free (Icons: CC BY 4.0, Fonts: SIL OFL 1.1, Code: MIT License) --\u003e\u003cpath d=\"M433.941 65.941l-51.882-51.882A48 48 0 0 0 348.118 0H176c-26.51 0-48 21.49-48 48v48H48c-26.51 0-48 21.49-48 48v320c0 26.51 21.49 48 48 48h224c26.51 0 48-21.49 48-48v-48h80c26.51 0 48-21.49 48-48V99.882a48 48 0 0 0-14.059-33.941zM266 464H54a6 6 0 0 1-6-6V150a6 6 0 0 1 6-6h74v224c0 26.51 21.49 48 48 48h96v42a6 6 0 0 1-6 6zm128-96H182a6 6 0 0 1-6-6V54a6 6 0 0 1 6-6h106v88c0 13.255 10.745 24 24 24h88v202a6 6 0 0 1-6 6zm6-256h-64V48h9.632c1.591 0 3.117.632 4.243 1.757l48.368 48.368a6 6 0 0 1 1.757 4.243V112z\"/\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\r\n          \u003cspan class=\"check-icon tw-hidden\"\u003e\u003csvg class=\"icon\"\n    xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 512 512\"\u003e\u003c!-- Font Awesome Free 5.15.4 by @fontawesome - https://fontawesome.com License - https://fontawesome.com/license/free (Icons: CC BY 4.0, Fonts: SIL OFL 1.1, Code: MIT License) --\u003e\u003cpath d=\"M173.898 439.404l-166.4-166.4c-9.997-9.997-9.997-26.206 0-36.204l36.203-36.204c9.997-9.998 26.207-9.998 36.204 0L192 312.69 432.095 72.596c9.997-9.997 26.207-9.997 36.204 0l36.203 36.204c9.997 9.997 9.997 26.206 0 36.204l-294.4 294.401c-9.998 9.997-26.207 9.997-36.204-.001z\"/\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\r\n      \u003c/button\u003e\r\n        \r\n      \u003cbutton \r\n        class=\"\r\n          tw-select-none \r\n          tw-mx-2 \r\n          tw-block \r\n          group-[.is-open]:tw-hidden \r\n          print:!tw-hidden\" \r\n        disabled\r\n        aria-hidden=\"true\"\u003e\u003csvg class=\"icon\"\n    xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 512 512\"\u003e\u003c!-- Font Awesome Free 5.15.4 by @fontawesome - https://fontawesome.com License - https://fontawesome.com/license/free (Icons: CC BY 4.0, Fonts: SIL OFL 1.1, Code: MIT License) --\u003e\u003cpath d=\"M328 256c0 39.8-32.2 72-72 72s-72-32.2-72-72 32.2-72 72-72 72 32.2 72 72zm104-72c-39.8 0-72 32.2-72 72s32.2 72 72 72 72-32.2 72-72-32.2-72-72-72zm-352 0c-39.8 0-72 32.2-72 72s32.2 72 72 72 72-32.2 72-72-32.2-72-72-72z\"/\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\u003c/button\u003e\r\n    \u003c/div\u003e\r\n  \u003c/div\u003e\r\n  \u003cpre style=\"counter-reset: codeblock;\" class=\"tw-block tw-m-0 tw-p-0\"\u003e\u003ccode \r\n    id=\"codeblock-id-31\" \r\n    class=\"\r\n      chroma \r\n      !tw-block \r\n      tw-p-0\r\n      tw-m-0\r\n      tw-transition-[max-height] \r\n      tw-duration-500 \r\n      tw-ease-in-out \r\n      group-[.is-closed]:!tw-max-h-0 \r\n      group-[.is-wrap]:tw-text-wrap\r\n      tw-overflow-y-hidden\r\n      tw-overflow-x-auto\r\n      tw-scrollbar-thin\r\n      \"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"line\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"cl\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"k\"\u003e\\documentclass\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"nb\"\u003e{\u003c/span\u003earticle\u003cspan class=\"nb\"\u003e}\u003c/span\u003e\n\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"line\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"cl\"\u003e\n\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"line\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"cl\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"c\"\u003e% A4 layout\n\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"line\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"cl\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"c\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"k\"\u003e\\usepackage\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"na\"\u003e[a4paper,margin=2.5cm]\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"nb\"\u003e{\u003c/span\u003egeometry\u003cspan class=\"nb\"\u003e}\u003c/span\u003e\n\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"line\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"cl\"\u003e\n\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"line\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"cl\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"c\"\u003e% Greek + English (UTF-8) with pdfLaTeX\n\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"line\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"cl\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"c\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"k\"\u003e\\usepackage\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"na\"\u003e[utf8]\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"nb\"\u003e{\u003c/span\u003einputenc\u003cspan class=\"nb\"\u003e}\u003c/span\u003e\n\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"line\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"cl\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"k\"\u003e\\usepackage\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"na\"\u003e[english,greek]\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"nb\"\u003e{\u003c/span\u003ebabel\u003cspan class=\"nb\"\u003e}\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\"c\"\u003e% switch with \\selectlanguage{greek} / {english}\n\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"line\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"cl\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"c\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\n\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"line\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"cl\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"c\"\u003e% Arrays and spacing\n\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"line\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"cl\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"c\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"k\"\u003e\\usepackage\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"nb\"\u003e{\u003c/span\u003earray\u003cspan class=\"nb\"\u003e}\u003c/span\u003e\n\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"line\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"cl\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"k\"\u003e\\renewcommand\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"nb\"\u003e{\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"k\"\u003e\\arraystretch\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"nb\"\u003e}{\u003c/span\u003e1.6\u003cspan class=\"nb\"\u003e}\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\"err\"\u003e%\u003c/span\u003e line spacing between rows\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/code\u003e\u003c/pre\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003eThe only command that needs explaining is \u003ccode\u003e\\renewcommand{\\arraystretch}{1.6}\u003c/code\u003e, which increases row height globally; you can add per-row extra space with \\[4pt] too.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe other commands just enable greek and english characters (or you can use XeLaTeX and polyglossia)\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch2 id=\"adding-xparse-package\" class=\"headerLink\"\u003e\r\n    \u003ca href=\"#adding-xparse-package\" class=\"header-mark\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e14 Adding xparse package\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"code-block highlight is-open show-line-numbers  tw-group tw-my-2\"\u003e\r\n  \u003cdiv class=\"\r\n    \r\n    tw-flex \r\n    tw-flex-row\r\n    tw-flex-1 \r\n    tw-justify-between \r\n    tw-w-full tw-bg-bgColor-secondary\r\n    \"\u003e      \r\n    \u003cbutton \r\n      class=\"\r\n        code-block-button\r\n        tw-mx-2 \r\n        tw-flex\r\n        tw-flex-row\r\n        tw-flex-1\"\r\n      aria-hidden=\"true\"\u003e\r\n          \u003cdiv class=\"group-[.is-open]:tw-rotate-90 tw-transition-[transform] tw-duration-500 tw-ease-in-out print:!tw-hidden tw-w-min tw-h-min tw-my-1 tw-mx-1\"\u003e\u003csvg class=\"icon\"\n    xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 320 512\"\u003e\u003c!-- Font Awesome Free 5.15.4 by @fontawesome - https://fontawesome.com License - https://fontawesome.com/license/free (Icons: CC BY 4.0, Fonts: SIL OFL 1.1, Code: MIT License) --\u003e\u003cpath d=\"M285.476 272.971L91.132 467.314c-9.373 9.373-24.569 9.373-33.941 0l-22.667-22.667c-9.357-9.357-9.375-24.522-.04-33.901L188.505 256 34.484 101.255c-9.335-9.379-9.317-24.544.04-33.901l22.667-22.667c9.373-9.373 24.569-9.373 33.941 0L285.475 239.03c9.373 9.372 9.373 24.568.001 33.941z\"/\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\r\n          \u003cp class=\"tw-select-none !tw-my-1\"\u003eLatex\u003c/p\u003e\r\n      \u003c/button\u003e\r\n\r\n   \u003cdiv class=\"tw-flex\"\u003e\r\n      \u003cbutton \r\n        class=\"\r\n          line-number-button\r\n          tw-mx-2 \r\n          tw-hidden \r\n          group-[.is-open]:tw-block \r\n          group-[.show-line-numbers]:tw-text-fgColor-link \r\n          print:!tw-hidden\" \r\n        title=\"Toggle line numbers\"\u003e\u003csvg class=\"icon\"\n    xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 512 512\"\u003e\u003c!-- Font Awesome Free 5.15.4 by @fontawesome - https://fontawesome.com License - https://fontawesome.com/license/free (Icons: CC BY 4.0, Fonts: SIL OFL 1.1, Code: MIT License) --\u003e\u003cpath d=\"M61.77 401l17.5-20.15a19.92 19.92 0 0 0 5.07-14.19v-3.31C84.34 356 80.5 352 73 352H16a8 8 0 0 0-8 8v16a8 8 0 0 0 8 8h22.83a157.41 157.41 0 0 0-11 12.31l-5.61 7c-4 5.07-5.25 10.13-2.8 14.88l1.05 1.93c3 5.76 6.29 7.88 12.25 7.88h4.73c10.33 0 15.94 2.44 15.94 9.09 0 4.72-4.2 8.22-14.36 8.22a41.54 41.54 0 0 1-15.47-3.12c-6.49-3.88-11.74-3.5-15.6 3.12l-5.59 9.31c-3.72 6.13-3.19 11.72 2.63 15.94 7.71 4.69 20.38 9.44 37 9.44 34.16 0 48.5-22.75 