en\r\n          group-[.is-open]:tw-block\r\n          hover:tw-text-fgColor-link \r\n          print:!tw-hidden\"\r\n        title=\"Copy code\"\u003e\r\n          \u003cspan class=\"copy-icon tw-block\"\u003e\u003csvg class=\"icon\"\n    xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 448 512\"\u003e\u003c!-- Font Awesome Free 5.15.4 by @fontawesome - https://fontawesome.com License - https://fontawesome.com/license/free (Icons: CC BY 4.0, Fonts: SIL OFL 1.1, Code: MIT License) --\u003e\u003cpath d=\"M433.941 65.941l-51.882-51.882A48 48 0 0 0 348.118 0H176c-26.51 0-48 21.49-48 48v48H48c-26.51 0-48 21.49-48 48v320c0 26.51 21.49 48 48 48h224c26.51 0 48-21.49 48-48v-48h80c26.51 0 48-21.49 48-48V99.882a48 48 0 0 0-14.059-33.941zM266 464H54a6 6 0 0 1-6-6V150a6 6 0 0 1 6-6h74v224c0 26.51 21.49 48 48 48h96v42a6 6 0 0 1-6 6zm128-96H182a6 6 0 0 1-6-6V54a6 6 0 0 1 6-6h106v88c0 13.255 10.745 24 24 24h88v202a6 6 0 0 1-6 6zm6-256h-64V48h9.632c1.591 0 3.117.632 4.243 1.757l48.368 48.368a6 6 0 0 1 1.757 4.243V112z\"/\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\r\n          \u003cspan class=\"check-icon tw-hidden\"\u003e\u003csvg class=\"icon\"\n    xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 512 512\"\u003e\u003c!-- Font Awesome Free 5.15.4 by @fontawesome - https://fontawesome.com License - https://fontawesome.com/license/free (Icons: CC BY 4.0, Fonts: SIL OFL 1.1, Code: MIT License) --\u003e\u003cpath d=\"M173.898 439.404l-166.4-166.4c-9.997-9.997-9.997-26.206 0-36.204l36.203-36.204c9.997-9.998 26.207-9.998 36.204 0L192 312.69 432.095 72.596c9.997-9.997 26.207-9.997 36.204 0l36.203 36.204c9.997 9.997 9.997 26.206 0 36.204l-294.4 294.401c-9.998 9.997-26.207 9.997-36.204-.001z\"/\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\r\n      \u003c/button\u003e\r\n        \r\n      \u003cbutton \r\n        class=\"\r\n          tw-select-none \r\n          tw-mx-2 \r\n          tw-block \r\n          group-[.is-open]:tw-hidden \r\n          print:!tw-hidden\" \r\n        disabled\r\n        aria-hidden=\"true\"\u003e\u003csvg class=\"icon\"\n    xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 512 512\"\u003e\u003c!-- Font Awesome Free 5.15.4 by @fontawesome - https://fontawesome.com License - https://fontawesome.com/license/free (Icons: CC BY 4.0, Fonts: SIL OFL 1.1, Code: MIT License) --\u003e\u003cpath d=\"M328 256c0 39.8-32.2 72-72 72s-72-32.2-72-72 32.2-72 72-72 72 32.2 72 72zm104-72c-39.8 0-72 32.2-72 72s32.2 72 72 72 72-32.2 72-72-32.2-72-72-72zm-352 0c-39.8 0-72 32.2-72 72s32.2 72 72 72 72-32.2 72-72-32.2-72-72-72z\"/\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\u003c/button\u003e\r\n    \u003c/div\u003e\r\n  \u003c/div\u003e\r\n  \u003cpre style=\"counter-reset: codeblock;\" class=\"tw-block tw-m-0 tw-p-0\"\u003e\u003ccode \r\n    id=\"codeblock-id-32\" \r\n    class=\"\r\n      chroma \r\n      !tw-block \r\n      tw-p-0\r\n      tw-m-0\r\n      tw-transition-[max-height] \r\n      tw-duration-500 \r\n      tw-ease-in-out \r\n      group-[.is-closed]:!tw-max-h-0 \r\n      group-[.is-wrap]:tw-text-wrap\r\n      tw-overflow-y-hidden\r\n      tw-overflow-x-auto\r\n      tw-scrollbar-thin\r\n      \"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"line\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"cl\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"k\"\u003e\\usepackage\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"nb\"\u003e{\u003c/span\u003exparse\u003cspan class=\"nb\"\u003e}\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/code\u003e\u003c/pre\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003eThe xparse package gives LaTeX a more powerful way to define commands and environments compared to the old \u003ccode\u003e\\newcommand\u003c/code\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eIt allows optional arguments with defaults, multiple types of arguments, key–value style arguments, etc.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eWithout it, \\newcommand is more limited (only mandatory args and one optional with a fixed default).\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003ePerfect 👌 Let’s break it all down step by step.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch3 id=\"1-usepackagexparse\" class=\"headerLink\"\u003e\r\n    \u003ca href=\"#1-usepackagexparse\" class=\"header-mark\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e14.1 1. \u003ccode\u003e\\usepackage{xparse}\u003c/code\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe \u003ccode\u003exparse\u003c/code\u003e package gives LaTeX a \u003cstrong\u003emore powerful way\u003c/strong\u003e to define commands and environments compared to the old \u003ccode\u003e\\newcommand\u003c/code\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eIt allows \u003cstrong\u003eoptional arguments with defaults\u003c/strong\u003e, multiple types of arguments, key–value style arguments, etc.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eWithout it, \u003ccode\u003e\\newcommand\u003c/code\u003e is more limited (only mandatory args and one optional with a fixed default).\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003ch3 id=\"2-newdocumentcommand-vs-newcommand\" class=\"headerLink\"\u003e\r\n    \u003ca href=\"#2-newdocumentcommand-vs-newcommand\" class=\"header-mark\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e14.2 2. \u003ccode\u003e\\NewDocumentCommand\u003c/code\u003e vs \u003ccode\u003e\\newcommand\u003c/code\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ccode\u003e\\newcommand{\\foo}[2][default]{...}\u003c/code\u003e → only supports:\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eup to 9 arguments\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eat most one optional argument\u003c/strong\u003e (and it must be the first one)\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ccode\u003e\\NewDocumentCommand{\\foo}{argument-spec}{...}\u003c/code\u003e → supports:\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eunlimited arguments\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eoptional arguments \u003cstrong\u003eanywhere\u003c/strong\u003e in the argument list\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003emultiple defaults, star forms, key–value, etc.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003emuch clearer specification syntax\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eSo we use \u003ccode\u003e\\NewDocumentCommand\u003c/code\u003e because it’s \u003cstrong\u003emore expressive\u003c/strong\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch2 id=\"creating-the-first-iteration-of-digitbox\" class=\"headerLink\"\u003e\r\n    \u003ca href=\"#creating-the-first-iteration-of-digitbox\" class=\"header-mark\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e15 Creating the first iteration of digitbox\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"code-block highlight is-open show-line-numbers  tw-group tw-my-2\"\u003e\r\n  \u003cdiv class=\"\r\n    \r\n    tw-flex \r\n    tw-flex-row\r\n    tw-flex-1 \r\n    tw-justify-between \r\n    tw-w-full tw-bg-bgColor-secondary\r\n    \"\u003e      \r\n    \u003cbutton \r\n      class=\"\r\n        code-block-button\r\n        tw-mx-2 \r\n        tw-flex\r\n        tw-flex-row\r\n        tw-flex-1\"\r\n      aria-hidden=\"true\"\u003e\r\n          \u003cdiv class=\"group-[.is-open]:tw-rotate-90 tw-transition-[transform] tw-duration-500 tw-ease-in-out print:!tw-hidden tw-w-min tw-h-min tw-my-1 tw-mx-1\"\u003e\u003csvg class=\"icon\"\n    xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 320 512\"\u003e\u003c!-- Font Awesome Free 5.15.4 by @fontawesome - https://fontawesome.com License - https://fontawesome.com/license/free (Icons: CC BY 4.0, Fonts: SIL OFL 1.1, Code: MIT License) --\u003e\u003cpath d=\"M285.476 272.971L91.132 467.314c-9.373 9.373-24.569 9.373-33.941 0l-22.667-22.667c-9.357-9.357-9.375-24.522-.04-33.901L188.505 256 34.484 101.255c-9.335-9.379-9.317-24.544.04-33.901l22.667-22.667c9.373-9.373 24.569-9.373 33.941 0L285.475 239.03c9.373 9.372 9.373 24.568.001 33.941z\"/\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\r\n          \u003cp class=\"tw-select-none !tw-my-1\"\u003elatex\u003c/p\u003e\r\n      \u003c/button\u003e\r\n\r\n   \u003cdiv class=\"tw-flex\"\u003e\r\n      \u003cbutton \r\n        class=\"\r\n          line-number-button\r\n          tw-mx-2 \r\n          tw-hidden \r\n          group-[.is-open]:tw-block \r\n          group-[.show-line-numbers]:tw-text-fgColor-link \r\n          print:!tw-hidden\" \r\n        title=\"Toggle line numbers\"\u003e\u003csvg class=\"icon\"\n    xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 512 512\"\u003e\u003c!-- Font Awesome Free 5.15.4 by @fontawesome - https://fontawesome.com License - https://fontawesome.com/license/free (Icons: CC BY 4.0, Fonts: SIL OFL 1.1, Code: MIT License) --\u003e\u003cpath d=\"M61.77 401l17.5-20.15a19.92 19.92 0 0 0 5.07-14.19v-3.31C84.34 356 80.5 352 73 352H16a8 8 0 0 0-8 8v16a8 8 0 0 0 8 8h22.83a157.41 157.41 0 0 0-11 12.31l-5.61 7c-4 5.07-5.25 10.13-2.8 14.88l1.05 1.93c3 5.76 6.29 7.88 12.25 7.88h4.73c10.33 0 15.94 2.44 15.94 9.09 0 4.72-4.2 8.22-14.36 8.22a41.54 41.54 0 0 1-15.47-3.12c-6.49-3.88-11.74-3.5-15.6 3.12l-5.59 9.31c-3.72 6.13-3.19 11.72 2.63 15.94 7.71 4.69 20.38 9.44 37 9.44 34.16 0 48.5-22.75 48.5-44.12-.03-14.38-9.12-29.76-28.73-34.88zM496 224H176a16 16 0 0 0-16 16v32a16 16 0 0 0 16 16h320a16 16 0 0 0 16-16v-32a16 16 0 0 0-16-16zm0-160H176a16 16 0 0 0-16 16v32a16 16 0 0 0 16 16h320a16 16 0 0 0 16-16V80a16 16 0 0 0-16-16zm0 320H176a16 16 0 0 0-16 16v32a16 16 0 0 0 16 16h320a16 16 0 0 0 16-16v-32a16 16 0 0 0-16-16zM16 160h64a8 8 0 0 0 8-8v-16a8 8 0 0 0-8-8H64V40a8 8 0 0 0-8-8H32a8 8 0 0 0-7.14 4.42l-8 16A8 8 0 0 0 24 64h8v64H16a8 8 0 0 0-8 8v16a8 8 0 0 0 8 8zm-3.91 160H80a8 8 0 0 0 8-8v-16a8 8 0 0 0-8-8H41.32c3.29-10.29 48.34-18.68 48.34-56.44 0-29.06-25-39.56-44.47-39.56-21.36 0-33.8 10-40.46 18.75-4.37 5.59-3 10.84 2.8 15.37l8.58 6.88c5.61 4.56 11 2.47 16.12-2.44a13.44 13.44 0 0 1 9.46-3.84c3.33 0 9.28 1.56 9.28 8.75C51 248.19 0 257.31 0 304.59v4C0 316 5.08 320 12.09 320z\"/\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\u003c/button\u003e\r\n\r\n      \u003cbutton \r\n        class=\"\r\n          wrap-code-button\r\n          tw-select-none \r\n          tw-mx-2 \r\n          tw-hidden \r\n          group-[.is-open]:tw-block \r\n          group-[.is-wrap]:tw-text-fgColor-link \r\n          print:!tw-hidden\" \r\n        title=\"Toggle code wrap\"\u003e\u003csvg class=\"icon\"\n    xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 448 512\"\u003e\u003c!-- Font Awesome Free 5.15.4 by @fontawesome - https://fontawesome.com License - https://fontawesome.com/license/free (Icons: CC BY 4.0, Fonts: SIL OFL 1.1, Code: MIT License) --\u003e\u003cpath d=\"M16 132h416c8.837 0 16-7.163 16-16V76c0-8.837-7.163-16-16-16H16C7.163 60 0 67.163 0 76v40c0 8.837 7.163 16 16 16zm0 160h416c8.837 0 16-7.163 16-16v-40c0-8.837-7.163-16-16-16H16c-8.837 0-16 7.163-16 16v40c0 8.837 7.163 16 16 16zm0 160h416c8.837 0 16-7.163 16-16v-40c0-8.837-7.163-16-16-16H16c-8.837 0-16 7.163-16 16v40c0 8.837 7.163 16 16 16z\"/\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\u003c/button\u003e\r\n      \r\n      \u003cbutton \r\n        class=\"\r\n          copy-code-button\r\n          tw-select-none\r\n          tw-mx-2 \r\n          tw-hidden\r\n          group-[.is-open]:tw-block\r\n          hover:tw-text-fgColor-link \r\n          print:!tw-hidden\"\r\n        title=\"Copy code\"\u003e\r\n          \u003cspan class=\"copy-icon tw-block\"\u003e\u003csvg class=\"icon\"\n    xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 448 512\"\u003e\u003c!-- Font Awesome Free 5.15.4 by @fontawesome - https://fontawesome.com License - https://fontawesome.com/license/free (Icons: CC BY 4.0, Fonts: SIL OFL 1.1, Code: MIT License) --\u003e\u003cpath d=\"M433.941 65.941l-51.882-51.882A48 48 0 0 0 348.118 0H176c-26.51 0-48 21.49-48 48v48H48c-26.51 0-48 21.49-48 48v320c0 26.51 21.49 48 48 48h224c26.51 0 48-21.49 48-48v-48h80c26.51 0 48-21.49 48-48V99.882a48 48 0 0 0-14.059-33.941zM266 464H54a6 6 0 0 1-6-6V150a6 6 0 0 1 6-6h74v224c0 26.51 21.49 48 48 48h96v42a6 6 0 0 1-6 6zm128-96H182a6 6 0 0 1-6-6V54a6 6 0 0 1 6-6h106v88c0 13.255 10.745 24 24 24h88v202a6 6 0 0 1-6 6zm6-256h-64V48h9.632c1.591 0 3.117.632 4.243 1.757l48.368 48.368a6 6 0 0 1 1.757 4.243V112z\"/\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\r\n          \u003cspan class=\"check-icon tw-hidden\"\u003e\u003csvg class=\"icon\"\n    xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 512 512\"\u003e\u003c!-- Font Awesome Free 5.15.4 by @fontawesome - https://fontawesome.com License - https://fontawesome.com/license/free (Icons: CC BY 4.0, Fonts: SIL OFL 1.1, Code: MIT License) --\u003e\u003cpath d=\"M173.898 439.404l-166.4-166.4c-9.997-9.997-9.997-26.206 0-36.204l36.203-36.204c9.997-9.998 26.207-9.998 36.204 0L192 312.69 432.095 72.596c9.997-9.997 26.207-9.997 36.204 0l36.203 36.204c9.997 9.997 9.997 26.206 0 36.204l-294.4 294.401c-9.998 9.997-26.207 9.997-36.204-.001z\"/\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\r\n      \u003c/button\u003e\r\n        \r\n      \u003cbutton \r\n        class=\"\r\n          tw-select-none \r\n          tw-mx-2 \r\n          tw-block \r\n          group-[.is-open]:tw-hidden \r\n          print:!tw-hidden\" \r\n        disabled\r\n        aria-hidden=\"true\"\u003e\u003csvg class=\"icon\"\n    xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 512 512\"\u003e\u003c!-- Font Awesome Free 5.15.4 by @fontawesome - https://fontawesome.com License - https://fontawesome.com/license/free (Icons: CC BY 4.0, Fonts: SIL OFL 1.1, Code: MIT License) --\u003e\u003cpath d=\"M328 256c0 39.8-32.2 72-72 72s-72-32.2-72-72 32.2-72 72-72 72 32.2 72 72zm104-72c-39.8 0-72 32.2-72 72s32.2 72 72 72 72-32.2 72-72-32.2-72-72-72zm-352 0c-39.8 0-72 32.2-72 72s32.2 72 72 72 72-32.2 72-72-32.2-72-72-72z\"/\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\u003c/button\u003e\r\n    \u003c/div\u003e\r\n  \u003c/div\u003e\r\n  \u003cpre style=\"counter-reset: codeblock;\" class=\"tw-block tw-m-0 tw-p-0\"\u003e\u003ccode \r\n    id=\"codeblock-id-33\" \r\n    class=\"\r\n      chroma \r\n      !tw-block \r\n      tw-p-0\r\n      tw-m-0\r\n      tw-transition-[max-height] \r\n      tw-duration-500 \r\n      tw-ease-in-out \r\n      group-[.is-closed]:!tw-max-h-0 \r\n      group-[.is-wrap]:tw-text-wrap\r\n      tw-overflow-y-hidden\r\n      tw-overflow-x-auto\r\n      tw-scrollbar-thin\r\n      \"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"line\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"cl\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"c\"\u003e% \\digitbox[\u0026lt;width\u0026gt;][\u0026lt;height\u0026gt;]  (defaults: 8mm x 10mm)\n\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"line\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"cl\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"c\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"k\"\u003e\\NewDocumentCommand\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"nb\"\u003e{\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"k\"\u003e\\digitbox\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"nb\"\u003e}{\u003c/span\u003eO\u003cspan class=\"nb\"\u003e{\u003c/span\u003e8mm\u003cspan class=\"nb\"\u003e}\u003c/span\u003e O\u003cspan class=\"nb\"\u003e{\u003c/span\u003e10mm\u003cspan class=\"nb\"\u003e}}{\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"c\"\u003e%\n\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"line\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"cl\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"c\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e  \u003cspan class=\"k\"\u003e\\begingroup\u003c/span\u003e\n\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"line\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"cl\"\u003e  \u003cspan class=\"k\"\u003e\\setlength\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"nb\"\u003e{\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"k\"\u003e\\fboxsep\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"nb\"\u003e}{\u003c/span\u003e0pt\u003cspan class=\"nb\"\u003e}\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"c\"\u003e% no inner padding\n\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"line\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"cl\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"c\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e  \u003cspan class=\"k\"\u003e\\fbox\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"nb\"\u003e{\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"k\"\u003e\\makebox\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"na\"\u003e[#1]\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"nb\"\u003e{\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"k\"\u003e\\rule\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"nb\"\u003e{\u003c/span\u003e0pt\u003cspan class=\"nb\"\u003e}{\u003c/span\u003e#2\u003cspan class=\"nb\"\u003e}}}\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"c\"\u003e%\n\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"line\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"cl\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"c\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e  \u003cspan class=\"k\"\u003e\\endgroup\u003c/span\u003e\n\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"line\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"cl\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"nb\"\u003e}\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/code\u003e\u003c/pre\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003ch3 id=\"1-the-o8mm-o10mm-in-newdocumentcommanddigitboxo8mm-o10mm\" class=\"headerLink\"\u003e\r\n    \u003ca href=\"#1-the-o8mm-o10mm-in-newdocumentcommanddigitboxo8mm-o10mm\" class=\"header-mark\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e15.1 1. The \u003ccode\u003eO{8mm} O{10mm}\u003c/code\u003e in \u003ccode\u003e\\NewDocumentCommand{\\digitbox}{O{8mm} O{10mm}}\u003c/code\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIn the argument specification,\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003ccode\u003eO{\u0026lt;default\u0026gt;}\u003c/code\u003e means \u003cstrong\u003eoptional argument with default value \u003ccode\u003e\u0026lt;default\u0026gt;\u003c/code\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eSo here:\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eFirst optional argument: width (default \u003ccode\u003e8mm\u003c/code\u003e)\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eSecond optional argument: height (default \u003ccode\u003e10mm\u003c/code\u003e)\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThat’s why you can call \u003ccode\u003e\\digitbox\u003c/code\u003e:\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003ccode\u003e\\digitbox\u003c/code\u003e → box of \u003ccode\u003e8mm × 10mm\u003c/code\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003ccode\u003e\\digitbox[12mm]\u003c/code\u003e → width \u003ccode\u003e12mm\u003c/code\u003e, height still \u003ccode\u003e10mm\u003c/code\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003ccode\u003e\\digitbox[12mm][15mm]\u003c/code\u003e → width \u003ccode\u003e12mm\u003c/code\u003e, height \u003ccode\u003e15mm\u003c/code\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003chr\u003e\n\u003ch3 id=\"2-fboxsep\" class=\"headerLink\"\u003e\r\n    \u003ca href=\"#2-fboxsep\" class=\"header-mark\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e15.2 2. \u003ccode\u003e\\fboxsep\u003c/code\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eLaTeX adds padding \u003cstrong\u003einside\u003c/strong\u003e framed boxes by default.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003ccode\u003e\\fboxsep\u003c/code\u003e is the \u003cstrong\u003elength of that padding\u003c/strong\u003e. Default is around \u003cstrong\u003e3pt\u003c/strong\u003e.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eSetting \u003ccode\u003e\\setlength{\\fboxsep}{0pt}\u003c/code\u003e removes the extra whitespace, so the frame hugs your content exactly.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eWithout this, the box would look oversized compared to digits.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003chr\u003e\n\u003ch3 id=\"3-make-the-actual-box-fboxmakebox1rule0pt2\" class=\"headerLink\"\u003e\r\n    \u003ca href=\"#3-make-the-actual-box-fboxmakebox1rule0pt2\" class=\"header-mark\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e15.3 3. Make the actual box: \u003ccode\u003e\\fbox{\\makebox[#1]{\\rule{0pt}{#2}}}\u003c/code\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cp\u003eLet’s dissect:\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ccode\u003e\\fbox{...}\u003c/code\u003e → draws a rectangular frame around its contents.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ccode\u003e\\makebox[#1]{...}\u003c/code\u003e → makes a box of width \u003ccode\u003e#1\u003c/code\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eIf contents are smaller, it pads (here empty).\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ccode\u003e\\rule{0pt}{#2}\u003c/code\u003e → makes an \u003cstrong\u003einvisible vertical rule\u003c/strong\u003e with:\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ewidth \u003ccode\u003e0pt\u003c/code\u003e (so not visible horizontally)\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eheight \u003ccode\u003e#2\u003c/code\u003e (so the box gets that much tall).\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eTogether:\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eWidth = \u003ccode\u003e#1\u003c/code\u003e (first argument, e.g. \u003ccode\u003e8mm\u003c/code\u003e)\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eHeight = \u003ccode\u003e#2\u003c/code\u003e (second argument, e.g. \u003ccode\u003e10mm\u003c/code\u003e)\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eContent is invisible, so you just see an empty framed box.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThat’s how we force \u003ccode\u003e\\fbox\u003c/code\u003e to have \u003cstrong\u003efixed dimensions\u003c/strong\u003e instead of shrinking to its contents.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch3 id=\"4-removing-the--from-the-commands-alters-the-result-why\" class=\"headerLink\"\u003e\r\n    \u003ca href=\"#4-removing-the--from-the-commands-alters-the-result-why\" class=\"header-mark\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e15.4 4. Removing the % from the commands alters the result. Why?\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cp\u003eYou will ask, isn\u0026rsquo;t \u003ccode\u003e%\u003c/code\u003e just for comments? Well yes, \u003ccode\u003e%\u003c/code\u003e is indeed the comment character in LaTeX. But in TeX, it has one \u003cem\u003eextra\u003c/em\u003e important side effect: it also \u003cstrong\u003eremoves the newline (or space) that follows it\u003c/strong\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch5 id=\"whats-going-on-here\" class=\"headerLink\"\u003e\r\n    \u003ca href=\"#whats-going-on-here\" class=\"header-mark\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e15.4.0.1 \u003cstrong\u003eWhat’s going on here?\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h5\u003e\u003cp\u003eLet’s look at our code:\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"code-block highlight is-open show-line-numbers  tw-group tw-my-2\"\u003e\r\n  \u003cdiv class=\"\r\n    \r\n    tw-flex \r\n    tw-flex-row\r\n    tw-flex-1 \r\n    tw-justify-between \r\n    tw-w-full tw-bg-bgColor-secondary\r\n    \"\u003e      \r\n    \u003cbutton \r\n      class=\"\r\n        code-block-button\r\n        tw-mx-2 \r\n        tw-flex\r\n        tw-flex-row\r\n        tw-flex-1\"\r\n      aria-hidden=\"true\"\u003e\r\n          \u003cdiv class=\"group-[.is-open]:tw-rotate-90 tw-transition-[transform] tw-duration-500 tw-ease-in-out print:!tw-hidden tw-w-min tw-h-min tw-my-1 tw-mx-1\"\u003e\u003csvg class=\"icon\"\n    xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 320 512\"\u003e\u003c!-- Font Awesome Free 5.15.4 by @fontawesome - https://fontawesome.com License - https://fontawesome.com/license/free (Icons: CC BY 4.0, Fonts: SIL OFL 1.1, Code: MIT License) --\u003e\u003cpath d=\"M285.476 272.971L91.132 467.314c-9.373 9.373-24.569 9.373-33.941 0l-22.667-22.667c-9.357-9.357-9.375-24.522-.04-33.901L188.505 256 34.484 101.255c-9.335-9.379-9.317-24.544.04-33.901l22.667-22.667c9.373-9.373 24.569-9.373 33.941 0L285.475 239.03c9.373 9.372 9.373 24.568.001 33.941z\"/\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\r\n          \u003cp class=\"tw-select-none !tw-my-1\"\u003elatex\u003c/p\u003e\r\n      \u003c/button\u003e\r\n\r\n   \u003cdiv class=\"tw-flex\"\u003e\r\n      \u003cbutton \r\n        class=\"\r\n          line-number-button\r\n          tw-mx-2 \r\n          tw-hidden \r\n          group-[.is-open]:tw-block \r\n          group-[.show-line-numbers]:tw-text-fgColor-link \r\n          print:!tw-hidden\" \r\n        title=\"Toggle line numbers\"\u003e\u003csvg class=\"icon\"\n    xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 512 512\"\u003e\u003c!-- Font Awesome Free 5.15.4 by @fontawesome - https://fontawesome.com License - https://fontawesome.com/license/free (Icons: CC BY 4.0, Fonts: SIL OFL 1.1, Code: MIT License) --\u003e\u003cpath d=\"M61.77 401l17.5-20.15a19.92 19.92 0 0 0 5.07-14.19v-3.31C84.34 356 80.5 352 73 352H16a8 8 